imdb.plot outline: Great American Car War is a competition reality TV show that pits tuner teams with late model Mustangs vs. Camaros. It is the classic battle of Ford vs. Chevy. The two teams of expert tuners have limited budgets and time to improve the performance and appearance of their respective cars. Winne of the most competitions win the coveted Car War Trophy. Jessica Barton Hosts.
imdb.title: The Great American Car War
